{"tid":2262090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利迷講到做到 真係要人地死全家","createTime":"2020-10-28T22:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T00:35:35.000Z","uid":5655,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"afb3a76aafe70922c83f8652f2401cfbfc66f646","tid":2262090,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:17:34.000Z","msg":"在月中的默西塞德郡打吡出現爭議的一幕，愛華頓門將碧福特在一次爭球中對雲迪克施展較剪腳，導致他十字韌帶受傷，預計傷出整季。賽後大批利物浦球迷對碧福特口誅筆伐，外媒報導，基於事態嚴重，碧福特在近日決定聘請保鑣保護家人安全。<br />\n<br />\n打吡戰開賽僅5分鐘，碧福特就以一記粗野的較剪腳攔截踢傷雲迪克，但因為對方事前越位在先，因此攔截動作無被吹罰，碧福特全場踢足90分鐘。賽後英超賽會宣佈，由於球證和VAR裁判在比賽期間已經檢視過攔截動作，認為碧福特不足以被紅牌驅逐離場，根據賽例和程序，賽會不能夠覆核這次攔截，因此碧福特全身而回，這記「收山腳」不獲追究，他在之後對修咸頓一戰繼續正選把關。<br />\n<br />\n利迷浦球迷當然不滿此判決，事後在網上攻擊碧福特和他的家人，輕則人身攻擊，重的更涉及死亡恐嚇。外媒報導，碧福特本來認為「球場事，球場了。」，低估事態的嚴重性，但由於死亡恐嚇持續，他最終決定聘請保安公司24小時保護自己和家人的人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.fanpiece.com/m/cornerflagnews/c1388000.html?page=football&amp;fbclid=IwAR2l0SDNT_Ro6defareH7Kteei79knB8mkhzZBAofHFt58PysB31sxRUGxI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fcornerflagnews%2Fc1388000.html%3Fpage%3Dfootball%26fbclid%3DIwAR2l0SDNT_Ro6defareH7Kteei79knB8mkhzZBAofHFt58PysB31sxRUGxI&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KinyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=1c06298d\" target=\"_blank\">https://football.fanpiece.com/m/cornerflagnews/c1388000.html?page=football&amp;fbclid=IwAR2l0SDNT_Ro6defareH7Kteei79knB8mkhzZBAofHFt58PysB31sxRUGxI</a>"},{"pid":"9b787157067261b32666fe2c3cec7dc97bf86384","tid":2262090,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:18:05.000Z","msg":"空難....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca019d552fc2ba8551f18df0f344261e8eae4f2","tid":2262090,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b787157067261b32666fe2c3cec7dc97bf86384","tid":2262090,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:18:05.000Z","msg":"空難....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:35:35.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}